schema.description: This view contains finance accounting customer open items.  It joins data from bkpf and bseg tables and filters for open items that are not cleared and have a posting key of 'D'. The data is at the line item level of the accounting document.

formula.value:
CASE
    WHEN BSEG.shkzg = 'S' THEN BSEG.dmbtr  -- S = Debit | Amount in document currency
    WHEN BSEG.shkzg = 'H' THEN BSEG.dmbtr * -1  -- H = Credit | Amount in document currency
    ELSE BSEG.dmbtr
  END

CASE
    WHEN BSEG.shkzg = 'S' THEN BSEG.wrbtr  -- S = Debit | Amount in document currency
    WHEN BSEG.shkzg = 'H' THEN BSEG.wrbtr * -1  -- H = Credit | Amount in document currency
    ELSE BSEG.wrbtr
  END
